ğŸ¤– STEP 3: SPAWN AND QUEUE AGENTS

âœ… 3.1 Open Cursor and the project
Wait for full index and .cursor/ parsing.

âœ… 3.2 Spawn each Background Agent
For each task group:

Press Ctrl + E â†’ New Background Agent
Name it (auth-agent, analytics-ui-agent, etc.)
Cursor creates a branch for that agent: feature/auth-agent
Paste your first prompt (from your task file)

âš ï¸ TROUBLESHOOTING: If agent gets stuck on interactive prompts:
- Check Background Agent panel logs
- Look for prompts like "Proceed? (Y/n)"
- Cancel agent and respawn with fixed environment.json

âœ… 3.3 Queue follow-up prompts
While the agent is running, queue steps like:

